Retrieve a user by username and/or email

The user will be returned only if it belongs to the calling site

Examples:
    >>> get_edxapp_user(
        {
            "username": "Bob",
            "site": request.site
        }
    )
    >>> get_edxapp_user(
        {
            "email": "Bob@mailserver.com",
            "site": request.site
        }
    )

